{"id":"lyr_6ZmI5oWn55Cz_NDcwMQ_0034","text":"來生跟你對換彼此意識可不可","structure":{"line_index":34,"char_count":13},"semantics":{"themes":["交換","來生","意識"],"sentiment":"NEUTRAL","keywords":["來生","對換","意識"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[0,3,3,5,4,2,9,9,4,3,9,3,9],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["loi4","sang1","gan1","nei5","deoi3","wun6","bei2","ci2","ji3","sik1","ho2","bat1","ho2"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"來生","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"跟","pos":"ADP"},{"text":"你","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"對換","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"彼此","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"意識","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"可","pos":"AUX"},{"text":"不可","pos":"ADV"}],"syntax_notes":"將「角色」替換為「意識」，更深入地探討了來生交換的可能性，帶有哲學意味。"},"source":{"title":"請放心傷我","artists":["陳慧琳"],"lyricists":["小克"],"year":0,"genre":["Mandopop","Cantopop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_4701","prev_line_id":"lyr_6ZmI5oWn55Cz_NDcwMQ_0033","next_line_id":"lyr_6ZmI5oWn55Cz_NDcwMQ_0035","paragraph_id":"para_12"}}
{"id":"lyr_6ZmI5oWn55Cz_NDcwMQ_0035","text":"讓我嘗痛楚 請求蒼天的許可","structure":{"line_index":35,"char_count":12},"semantics":{"themes":["承受痛苦","請求","許可"],"sentiment":"NEGATIVE","keywords":["嘗痛楚","請求","許可"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[2,5,0,4,9,9,0,3,3,3,9,9],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["joeng6","ngo5","soeng4","tung3","co2","cing2","kau4","cong1","tin1","dik1","heoi2","ho2"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"讓","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"我","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"嘗","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"痛楚","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"請求","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"蒼天","pos":"PROPN"},{"text":"的","pos":"PART"},{"text":"許可","pos":"NOUN"}],"syntax_notes":"「請求蒼天的許可」將承受痛苦的願望提升到一個更高的層次，帶有宿命和無奈。"},"source":{"title":"請放心傷我","artists":["陳慧琳"],"lyricists":["小克"],"year":0,"genre":["Mandopop","Cantopop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_4701","prev_line_id":"lyr_6ZmI5oWn55Cz_NDcwMQ_0034","next_line_id":"lyr_6ZmI5oWn55Cz_NDcwMQ_0036","paragraph_id":"para_12"}}
{"id":"lyr_6ZmI5oWn55Cz_NDcwMQ_0036","text":"如果可以愛奉還 請你丟低我","structure":{"line_index":36,"char_count":12},"semantics":{"themes":["請求","傷害","放手"],"sentiment":"NEGATIVE","keywords":["愛奉還","丟低我"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[0,9,9,5,4,2,0,9,5,3,3,5],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["jyu4","gwo2","ho2","ji5","oi3","fung6","waan4","cing2","nei5","diu1","dai1","ngo5"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"如果","pos":"CONJ"},{"text":"可以","pos":"AUX"},{"text":"愛","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"奉還","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"請","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"你","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"丟","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"低","pos":"PART"},{"text":"我","pos":"PRON"}],"syntax_notes":"「請你丟低我」是更直接的請求，希望對方能放手，結束這段關係，與「放心傷我」的情感有所不同。"},"source":{"title":"請放心傷我","artists":["陳慧琳"],"lyricists":["小克"],"year":0,"genre":["Mandopop","Cantopop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_4701","prev_line_id":"lyr_6ZmI5oWn55Cz_NDcwMQ_0035","next_line_id":"lyr_6ZmI5oWn55Cz_NDcwMQ_0037","paragraph_id":"para_12"}}
{"id":"lyr_6ZmI5oWn55Cz_NDcwMQ_0037","text":"如果再遇你於銀河 求這個後果","structure":{"line_index":37,"char_count":13},"semantics":{"themes":["重逢","期望","後果"],"sentiment":"NEUTRAL","keywords":["再遇","銀河","後果"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[0,9,4,2,5,3,0,0,0,5,4,2,9],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["jyu4","gwo2","zoi3","jyu6","nei5","jyu1","ngan4","ho4","kau4","ze5","go3","hau6","gwo2"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"如果","pos":"CONJ"},{"text":"再遇","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"你","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"於銀河","pos":"ADP"},{"text":"求","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"這個","pos":"DET"},{"text":"後果","pos":"NOUN"}],"syntax_notes":"「如果再遇你於銀河，求這個後果」以浪漫的想像結尾，將重逢的期望寄託於遙遠的未來，並帶有一絲對未知後果的探求。"},"source":{"title":"請放心傷我","artists":["陳慧琳"],"lyricists":["小克"],"year":0,"genre":["Mandopop","Cantopop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_4701","prev_line_id":"lyr_6ZmI5oWn55Cz_NDcwMQ_0036","next_line_id":null,"paragraph_id":"para_13"}}
